      <caption>
        <p>Box-and-whisker plots of tFAM scores by eubacterial taxon, after standardization of TFAM scores by their tDNA identity class. Boxes show the interquartile range and median. Whiskers extend to 1.5 times the interquartile range. Plusses (+) show outliers.</p>
